@bazinac Ok, that does seem to narrow it down to TF a bit more. I think it'd help to know more about your graph topology. What are unique nodes on the path to final_result_B that don't connect to final_result_A? What are the types/dimensions? Can you run quantize_graph with just final_result_B and then query it at runtime?

@petewarden Do you know of any issues involving quantization with multiple outputs?
